r=#A62A2A>(8/20/02 9:14:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2579.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Language Question</span><hr size=1> Greetings,<br>
<br>
I have a question regarding learning languages.  I noticed that I only have a handful of languages available at my trainer.  Each one of them gave me the message that I learned the basics of the skill when I put one training point in it.<br>
<br>
Do you have to learn the basics in each language before you make advancements in it?<br>
<br>
If the answer is yes, where do I go to learn the basics of each language that is not offered by my trainer.  As a note, I am a Half Elf Bard and I have travelled to Freeport, Qeynos, Kelethin, and Shar Vahl.  All have given me the same list of languages that I can learn from them.<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
Xaman<br>
Bard of the 14th Song<br>
